# BZ Reaction Differential Equations

This repository now includes:

- `BZ_simulation_design.md`: mathematical design notes for Oregonator ODE/PDE modeling.
- `src/bz_simulation.cpp`: a starter C++ reaction–diffusion simulator that writes PPM frames.

## Build

```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -O2 -o bz_sim src/bz_simulation.cpp
```

## Run

```bash
./bz_sim
```

The simulation writes `frame_XXXXX.ppm` images. Convert to video:

```bash
ffmpeg -framerate 20 -i frame_%05d.ppm -pix_fmt yuv420p bz.mp4
```
